      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEAR DARLING (2) has been tackling higher-graded races than this of late so should find this more to her liking. Has the speed to to take advantage of the low draw so has winning claims. FEISTY TIGER (7) scored at Canberra two starts back then did a great job again at her latest appearance over 1660m at Parkes, beaten only 1.75 metres into third after being up on the pace from the outset. Drawn to enjoy a nice run, with luck possibly playing a role at some point. Tackles a similar assignment and she can take this out. SINFUL KISS (10) finished fifth last start over 1660m at Parkes, beaten 6 metres, after a modest fourth at Parkes the run prior. Will need an ounce of luck to slot in from this tricky draw. Big chance if anywhere near her best. VIOLET JAY (8) must be included on the back of some solid recent form, most recently when fifth at Parkes over 1660m.",
